cart ( hangul : &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ; rr : &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ) is a 2014 south korean film directed by boo ji-young . about employees of a retail supermarket who band together when the contract workers are laid off , it is both an ensemble drama and a social critique . it made its world premiere in the city to city : seoul sidebar of the 2014 toronto international film festival . cart will also screen at the 19th busan international film festival and the 34th hawaii international film festival .